P & U to announce charges , cost savings in H2 . Swedish - U . S . drugs group Pharmacia & Upjohn Inc said on Tuesday it would announce charges and cost savings linked to its most recent round of restructuring in the second half of 1997 . Earlier this month the group ' s new president and chief executive officer Fred Hassan announced a series of initiatives aimed at simplifying P & U ' s complex international structure and its decision - making processes . These included creating a single , worldwide structure for operations including sales , marketing , research and development . - - London Newsroom + 44 171 542 7717 
